<p>
  There are several awarenesses here. They are all, in some way, you.
</p>

<p>
  You are also floating in greenness, still. You feel <i>aware</i> in several different places. Some of those
  awarenesses are floating in the Green.
</p>

<p>
  <a class='action-button' click-action='reach_out_one' click-action-args='<%= @current_character.name %>' href='#'>Reach out to one 'somebody?'</a>
